==English==

===Suffix===
'''[[nudge]] nudge [[wink]] wink'''
# phrase added at the end of the sentence to hint that the speaker is referring to something else. 
#:''Anyway, the reason I didn't answer the door was because I was in bed, nudge nudge wink wink''

====See Also====
*[[if you know what I mean]]

===Usage===
This is the equivalent of nudging someone and winking at them, which cannot be done in writing.